<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT55">
<l>kaṭaiṉiṉ ṟamarar kaḻaltoḻutu nāḷu</l>
<l>miṭaiṉiṉṟa viṉpatta rāvar puṭaiṉiṉṟa</l>
<l>nīrōta mēṉi neṭumālē niṉṉaṭiyai</l>
<l>yārōta vallā ravar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>People who stand at the entrance of [other] immortals [gods],</l>
<l>always worshipping [their] feet, will have intermediate joy.</l>
<l>O tall Māl with a body like the ocean-water that surrounds [the earth]!</l>
<l>Who is able to recite [the glories of] Your feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
